SPCOMBINE		14-Nov-88	(Pedro Gigoux)

This directory contains the code for the interactive combine task, for
one-dimensional spectra. The important files contained here are:

comrebin.x
debug.x
edit.x
expscale.x

idsm_keywrds.x		unmodified copy from onedspec$idsm_keywrds.x
idsmtn.h		unmodified copy from onedspec$idsmtn.h

lam2pix.x		lambda_to_pixel procedure copy from onedspec$t_rebin.x

load_hdr.x		unmodified copy from onedspec$load_hdr.x

mkpkg			mkpkg file

plot.x

rebin.x			copy of procedures from onedspec$t_dispcor.x

setdef.x
sort.x

spcombine.h		task include file

spcombine.key		interactive key menu

spcombine.par		parameter file

spcombine.x
struct.x

t_spcombine.x		main task procedure

x_spcombine.x		task declaration
